==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Loyalist
<hw>Loy"al*ist</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A person who adheres to his
sovereign or to the lawful authority; especially, one who maintains his
allegiance to his prince or government, and defends his cause in times
of revolt or revolution.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Loyally</ent>⟦br⟧
